Revision history for Data-Hash-Totals

0.10    Wed Nov 17 23:53:35 CST 2004

        [ENHANCEMENTS]
        * Can now put commas in your numeric values.

        [FIXES]
        * Sorting of values is now using C<cmp> instead of C<< <=> >>

0.02    Fri Oct 29 10:53:46 CDT 2004
        [ENHANCEMENTS]
        * Now exports as_table by default.

        * as_table() now sorts by ascending key as a subsort to descending
          value.

0.01    Thu Sep  9 21:54:02 CDT 2004
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

